<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Mon, 03 Jun 2024 14:07:39 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>面对日益严重的危机，内塔尼亚胡打出了他仅剩的一张牌</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-03/ty-article/.premium/faced-with-multiplying-crises-netanyahu-plays-the-only-card-he-has-left/0000018f-ddb6-d622-a1bf-dfb617640000</link><description>解散以色列议会将使内塔尼亚胡摆脱极右翼伙伴的否决，并朝着与哈马斯达成协议的方向迈进，同时避免法院关于征召极端正统派以色列人的爆炸性决定</description><pubDate>Mon, 03 Jun 2024 12:39:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-03/ty-article/.premium/faced-with-multiplying-crises-netanyahu-plays-the-only-card-he-has-left/0000018f-ddb6-d622-a1bf-dfb617640000</guid></item><item><title>作为国际刑事法院第一任首席检察官，以色列领导人仍然可以通过这种方式避免战争罪审判</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-06-03/ty-article-opinion/.premium/as-iccs-first-chief-prosecutor-heres-how-israeli-leaders-can-avoid-war-crimes-trial/0000018f-c9d7-db12-a3ff-cbf7fe470000</link><description>国际刑事法院检察官只有一种方法可以决定针对以色列总理内塔尼亚胡和国防部长加兰特的案件不可受理。问题是以色列及其司法系统是否愿意采取必要的行动</description><pubDate>Mon, 03 Jun 2024 12:32:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-06-03/ty-article-opinion/.premium/as-iccs-first-chief-prosecutor-heres-how-israeli-leaders-can-avoid-war-crimes-trial/0000018f-c9d7-db12-a3ff-cbf7fe470000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军队对战争期间 48 名加沙人死亡事件进行刑事调查，其中大部分是被拘留者</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-03/ty-article/.premium/idf-conducts-criminal-investigation-into-48-deaths-of-gazans-in-the-war-mostly-detainees/0000018f-dd46-db0d-a98f-dd4f27950000</link><description>以色列国防军宪兵已启动数十起涉及士兵行为的刑事调查，其中包括涉嫌抢劫、盗窃武器、暴力和不服从命令的案件。然而，尚未对涉及加沙死亡的案件提出任何指控</description><pubDate>Mon, 03 Jun 2024 10:44:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-03/ty-article/.premium/idf-conducts-criminal-investigation-into-48-deaths-of-gazans-in-the-war-mostly-detainees/0000018f-dd46-db0d-a98f-dd4f27950000</guid></item><item><title>以色列北部揭示了穿过戈兰高地的未知罗马道路</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/archaeology/2024-06-03/ty-article-magazine/unknown-roman-road-revealed-cutting-through-golan-heights/0000018f-dd32-d673-ab8f-fffa5d410000</link><description>为什么罗马人修建了一条从加利利海到叙利亚纳瓦的道路，完全忽略了途中的许多村庄？</description><pubDate>Mon, 03 Jun 2024 09:08:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/archaeology/2024-06-03/ty-article-magazine/unknown-roman-road-revealed-cutting-through-golan-heights/0000018f-dd32-d673-ab8f-fffa5d410000</guid></item><item><title>加沙边境基布兹发现疑似哈马斯自 10 月 7 日以来被谋杀的以色列人尸体</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-03/ty-article/.premium/body-of-murdered-israeli-presumed-hostage-since-oct-7-found-in-gaza-border-kibbutz/0000018f-dcff-d000-adbf-ddff22700000</link><description>以色列国防军宣布，10 月 7 日被哈马斯杀害的多列夫·雅胡德 (Dolev Yahoud) 的遗体在尼尔奥兹基布兹 (Kibbutz Nir ​​Oz) 被发现。雅胡德的妹妹阿贝尔与她的搭档阿里尔·科尼奥和他的兄弟大卫·科尼奥仍被哈马斯关押</description><pubDate>Mon, 03 Jun 2024 08:34:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-03/ty-article/.premium/body-of-murdered-israeli-presumed-hostage-since-oct-7-found-in-gaza-border-kibbutz/0000018f-dcff-d000-adbf-ddff22700000</guid></item><item><title>拉法过境点可能是巴勒斯坦权力机构返回加沙的催化剂</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-03/ty-article/.premium/the-rafah-crossing-may-be-the-catalyst-for-the-return-of-the-palestinian-authority-to-gaza/0000018f-db8a-dd44-a3ef-db8b55e90000</link><description>正如开罗代表团在最近关于重新开放过境点寻求援助的峰会上所说，拉法是“巴勒斯坦-埃及过境点”。尽管以色列试图抵抗，巴勒斯坦权力机构可能是管理过境点和加沙本身的唯一现实选择</description><pubDate>Mon, 03 Jun 2024 02:49:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-03/ty-article/.premium/the-rafah-crossing-may-be-the-catalyst-for-the-return-of-the-palestinian-authority-to-gaza/0000018f-db8a-dd44-a3ef-db8b55e90000</guid></item><item><title>失去控制：以色列在加沙缺乏进展波及黎巴嫩边境</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-03/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-distances-himself-from-the-cease-fire-deal-he-already-agreed-too/0000018f-da59-dbdb-a59f-db59468c0000</link><description>真主党在黎巴嫩方面的损失明显更高，因为他们对以色列北部深处进行了猛烈炮击。随着公众对以色列政府采取行动的压力越来越大，全面战争的可能性迫在眉睫，带来更大的破坏</description><pubDate>Mon, 03 Jun 2024 02:48:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-03/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-distances-himself-from-the-cease-fire-deal-he-already-agreed-too/0000018f-da59-dbdb-a59f-db59468c0000</guid></item><item><title>糟糕的计划，糟糕的情报：以色列如何袭击拥挤的拉法难民营，造成数十人死亡</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2024-06-03/ty-article-magazine/.premium/bad-planning-and-intel-how-israel-struck-crowded-rafah-refugee-camp-killing-dozens/0000018f-d90e-d673-ab8f-ffcef88d0000</link><description>以色列国防军澄清说，进行了初步检查，以确保两名哈马斯高级官员所在的院落内没有平民，但来自国防机构的消息人士估计，这次袭击的可怕后果是计划不周的结果</description><pubDate>Mon, 03 Jun 2024 02:47:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2024-06-03/ty-article-magazine/.premium/bad-planning-and-intel-how-israel-struck-crowded-rafah-refugee-camp-killing-dozens/0000018f-d90e-d673-ab8f-ffcef88d0000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡：哈马斯协议不会阻止加沙战斗，但允许暂时停火以释放人质</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-03/ty-article-live/strikes-reported-in-syria-blinken-speaks-to-gallant-and-gantz-about-cease-fire-deal/0000018f-dbc1-d573-af8f-dbffaabd0000</link><description>埃及：哈马斯称拜登关于加沙协议的提议“积极”，正在等待以色列回应 ■ 10 月 7 日遇害的以色列人尸体已找到至 16 日 ■ 伊朗最高领袖赞扬 10 月 7 日的袭击阻碍了以色列地区正常化的努力 ■ 以色列国防部长在与布林肯通话时表示，以色列正在考虑用巴勒斯坦人替代加沙的哈马斯</description><pubDate>Mon, 03 Jun 2024 01:47:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-03/ty-article-live/strikes-reported-in-syria-blinken-speaks-to-gallant-and-gantz-about-cease-fire-deal/0000018f-dbc1-d573-af8f-dbffaabd0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列女足在欧洲锦标赛上遭到亲巴勒斯坦抗议者的骚扰</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/sports/2024-06-02/ty-article/.premium/israeli-womens-soccer-team-harassed-by-pro-palestine-protesters-at-european-championship/0000018f-d9d8-dbdb-a59f-d9d9cdb00000</link><description>“当以色列正在进行种族灭绝时，苏格兰接待以色列女队是可耻的”：以色列足球运动员在格拉斯哥的这场有争议的比赛中被跟踪，拒绝进入训练场，并拒绝奏国歌</description><pubDate>Sun, 02 Jun 2024 20:21:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/sports/2024-06-02/ty-article/.premium/israeli-womens-soccer-team-harassed-by-pro-palestine-protesters-at-european-championship/0000018f-d9d8-dbdb-a59f-d9d9cdb00000</guid></item><item><title>选举民意调查：甘茨当选总理，反对党赢得69个席位，内塔尼亚胡赢得51个席位</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-02/ty-article/elections-poll-gantz-favored-as-pm-opposition-bloc-win-69-seats-over-netanyahus-51/0000018f-da36-d673-ab8f-fffe578a0000</link><description>38% 的受访者表示，他们认为甘茨会成为更好的总理，低于 1 月份的 46%；而 30% 的受访者支持内塔尼亚胡，高于上次民意调查的 24%</description><pubDate>Sun, 02 Jun 2024 19:32:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-02/ty-article/elections-poll-gantz-favored-as-pm-opposition-bloc-win-69-seats-over-netanyahus-51/0000018f-da36-d673-ab8f-fffe578a0000</guid></item><item><title>马尔代夫因加沙战争禁止以色列人入境</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-02/ty-article/maldives-to-ban-israelis-from-entering-the-country-over-the-war-in-gaza/0000018f-da12-d573-af8f-da7f1b890000</link><description>马尔代夫是一个与以色列没有正式外交关系的逊尼派穆斯林国家，由于公众对加沙战争的愤怒上升，马尔代夫决定禁止以色列护照持有者入境。该国是以色列人喜爱的旅游目的地，去年有近 11,000 人到访</description><pubDate>Sun, 02 Jun 2024 18:04:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-02/ty-article/maldives-to-ban-israelis-from-entering-the-country-over-the-war-in-gaza/0000018f-da12-d573-af8f-da7f1b890000</guid></item><item><title>邀请内塔尼亚胡到华盛顿，民主党领导人在背后捅了以色列自由派一刀</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-06-02/ty-article/.highlight/inviting-netanyahu-to-d-c-democratic-leaders-stabbed-israels-liberals-in-the-back/0000018f-d9ac-d5bc-a1bf-dfbca6210000</link><description>帮助内塔尼亚胡在国会发表讲话并不是“亲以色列”，因为他知道自10月7日以来，他一直没有时间会见在他的监督下被哈马斯入侵的任何以色列社区</description><pubDate>Sun, 02 Jun 2024 17:37:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-06-02/ty-article/.highlight/inviting-netanyahu-to-d-c-democratic-leaders-stabbed-israels-liberals-in-the-back/0000018f-d9ac-d5bc-a1bf-dfbca6210000</guid></item><item><title>以色列陷入战争第 240 天：埃及称以色列必须撤出拉法过境点</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-06-02/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-240-israel-must-pull-out-of-rafah-crossing-egypt-says/0000018f-d9d5-d5bc-a1bf-dff5d2560001</link><description>内塔尼亚胡高级顾问称拜登周五提出停火建议的演讲具有“政治性” ■ 接近总理的消息人士告诉《国土报》，内塔尼亚胡总理试图绕过国家调查委员会 10 月 7 日的正常程序 ■ 国防部长加兰特：以色列正在准备一个替代管理机构加沙挑战哈马斯 ■ 战争进入 240 天后您需要了解以下内容</description><pubDate>Sun, 02 Jun 2024 16:55:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-06-02/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-240-israel-must-pull-out-of-rafah-crossing-egypt-says/0000018f-d9d5-d5bc-a1bf-dff5d2560001</guid></item><item><title>需要几代人的时间才能恢复：演员迈克尔·道格拉斯 (Michael Douglas) 访问 10 月 7 日遭受严重损失的以色列基布兹</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-02/ty-article/.premium/actor-michael-douglas-visits-israeli-kibbutz-that-suffered-heavy-loses-on-oct-7/0000018f-d989-dbdb-a59f-d9c92c4b0000</link><description>这位奥斯卡获奖明星开始了他的以色列之旅，首先参观了加沙边境的贝埃里基布兹，10 月 7 日，这里有近 100 人被杀，另有 26 人被扣为人质，然后前往特拉维夫参加摄影展</description><pubDate>Sun, 02 Jun 2024 16:44:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-02/ty-article/.premium/actor-michael-douglas-visits-israeli-kibbutz-that-suffered-heavy-loses-on-oct-7/0000018f-d989-dbdb-a59f-d9c92c4b0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列前外交部长兼副总理戴维·利维去世，享年 86 岁</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-02/ty-article/.premium/david-levy-former-israeli-foreign-minister-and-deputy-pm-dies-at-86/00000189-9cf1-d00f-a7db-bdfbe8af0000</link><description>作为利库德集团前领导人，利维在议会任职四十年，并担任外交部长、住房部长以及回归和一体化部长。作为 2018 年以色列奖获得者，利维“是最早表达许多人对分配和社会正义要求的人之一”</description><pubDate>Sun, 02 Jun 2024 16:24:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-02/ty-article/.premium/david-levy-former-israeli-foreign-minister-and-deputy-pm-dies-at-86/00000189-9cf1-d00f-a7db-bdfbe8af0000</guid></item><item><title>“我们永远拥有墨西哥”：以色列国家足球队在 1970 年世界杯上表现出色的不为人知的故事</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/culture/leisure/2024-06-02/ty-article-magazine/.premium/the-untold-story-of-israels-marvelous-national-soccer-team-in-the-1970-world-cup/0000018f-d8a2-d513-a9af-fef2301a0000</link><description>一部以色列电视连续剧以新的视角展示了足球领域的独特成就，同时也展示了“以色列充满自豪感、感觉无所不能、在世界上超级受欢迎”的时代</description><pubDate>Sun, 02 Jun 2024 15:45:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/culture/leisure/2024-06-02/ty-article-magazine/.premium/the-untold-story-of-israels-marvelous-national-soccer-team-in-the-1970-world-cup/0000018f-d8a2-d513-a9af-fef2301a0000</guid></item><item><title>“不投降，不向美国压力，不向任何事情投降”：内塔尼亚胡部长在纽约断然拒绝拜登停火提议</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-06-02/ty-article/.premium/thousands-calling-for-immediate-hostage-deal-will-lead-new-yorks-israel-day-parade/0000018f-d8da-d513-a9af-fefabceb0000</link><description>在纽约的以色列日游行中，超过 3,000 名游行者与人质家属一起呼吁立即达成协议，释放加沙哈马斯扣押的人质。美国多数党领袖查克·舒默在游行前表示，“在把他们带回家之前，我们决不能退缩”</description><pubDate>Sun, 02 Jun 2024 13:39:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-06-02/ty-article/.premium/thousands-calling-for-immediate-hostage-deal-will-lead-new-yorks-israel-day-parade/0000018f-d8da-d513-a9af-fefabceb0000</guid></item><item><title>拜登令人震惊的停火和人质协议提案旨在结束以色列与哈马斯在加沙的战争</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-02/ty-article/.premium/inside-bidens-shock-cease-fire-and-hostage-deal-proposal-to-end-israel-hamas-war-in-gaza/0000018f-d8ca-d513-a9af-fefa73210000</link><description>无论美国总统乔·拜登周五宣布的停火提案来自华盛顿还是耶路撒冷，现在很明显，全世界都将结束加沙战争的尝试视为“拜登的协议”，而他则将自己置于危险之中，就像从未</description><pubDate>Sun, 02 Jun 2024 13:29:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-02/ty-article/.premium/inside-bidens-shock-cease-fire-and-hostage-deal-proposal-to-end-israel-hamas-war-in-gaza/0000018f-d8ca-d513-a9af-fefa73210000</guid></item><item><title>真正的影响还是表演性的行动主义？ 《All Eyes on Rafah》如何在 Instagram 上引起轰动</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-02/ty-article/.premium/how-all-eyes-on-rafah-became-an-instagram-sensation/0000018f-d854-dbdb-a59f-d95d9d220000</link><description>这张由人工智能生成的图像在一周内被分享了近 5000 万次，在中东引起了赞扬和批评，也遭到了以色列影响者的反攻</description><pubDate>Sun, 02 Jun 2024 12:56:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-02/ty-article/.premium/how-all-eyes-on-rafah-became-an-instagram-sensation/0000018f-d854-dbdb-a59f-d95d9d220000</guid></item></channel></rss>